      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, really captures the atmosphere. To make the scene even more realistic, I need to start introducing some characters into this environment. Can you describe a few people who might be loitering on the corner or walking through this area? I want to get a sense of what the \"locals\" look like and how they're behaving—just give me some specific details on their appearance and the kind of vibe they give off to a stranger walking through.",
